you can get the latest sources from 
ftp://edhs1.gsfc.nasa.gov/edhs/hdfeos/latest_release
or
http://hdfeos.org (confusing!!!)

Example install setup:

- local dependancies
szip - not used yet
hdf4

setenv LINUX_BRAND linux64

tar xzf HDF-EOS2.18v1.00.tar.Z
cd hdfeos
bin/INSTALL-HDFEOS -i /disk01/home/swdev/ocssw/lib3_64/hdf4/include -l /disk01/home/swdev/ocssw/lib3_64/hdf4/lib
mv lib include ..
cd ..
rm -rf hdfeos



other options

bin/INSTALL-HDFEOS -i /disk01/home/swdev/ocssw/lib3_64/hdf4/include -l /disk01/home/swdev/ocssw/lib3_64/hdf4/lib -szi /disk01/home/swdev/ocssw/lib3_64/hdf4/include -szl /disk01/home/swdev/ocssw/lib3_64/hdf4/lib
